body.description: This space-saving Tot Tutors Kids Toy Storage Organizer with 12 Plastic Bins stores lots of children's toys in easy-to-see, easy-to-access plastic bins. The 8 standard and 4 large easy access storage containers are removable, making it fun for kids to take out toys, books, and games for playtime and quick to clean up after. This toy storage box alternative helps keep your little one’s room clean while at the same time the bins can teach color identification as well as sorting and cognitive skills. The height of the bins in this toy organizer is just right for toddlers and preschool-aged children. This piece of furniture is a great fit for all homes, whether large or small. This toy storage organizer comes in multiple color options to complement the existing furniture in your home as well as the table and chairs sets and other toy storage organizer products in Tot Tutors’ line of kids furniture. Color options include Primary Collection: natural finish with primary bins (red, green, blue, yellow); Pastel Collection: white finish with pastel bins (pink, light green, baby blue, light yellow); Espresso Collection: espresso finish with white bins; Summit Collection: white finish with primary color bins (red, green, blue, yellow); Friends: White finish with pink and purple bins (pink, purple, dark pink, white). Product sizing –34""W x 11""D (15.5""D with stabilizing braces) x 31""HStandard bins: 11.75""L x 8.25""W x 5.25""HLarge bins: 16""L x 11.75""W x 5.25""HAdditional primary colored plastic bins are also sold separately. Tot Tutors offers a full line of children’s furniture, organizational basics, and storage solutions. We have multiple room collections that fit the style of any home. Our children’s table and chairs, toy storage organizers, toy boxes, bookcases, beds, and upholstered chairs blend with all of your home’s furniture. Whether it’s the living room, playroom, or your child’s bedroom, Tot Tutors has just the right product to help your family grow.

We've since expanded our product catalog to provide families with comprehensive solutions for kids furniture, storage and play spaces. To date, we've sold millions of items across our catalog in the 25 years we've been in business, with over 50,000 reviews and an average 4.5 star rating. Our reputation as a company is built by focusing on creating products with a purpose: to turn homes into havens of comfort and style while helping make life better for others through our educational scholarships and charitable giving.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on August 7, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great overall value for the price and pretty pastel color sturdy bins are great !!
reviews.reviewText: I first would like to say I very rarely write reviews but I was so impressed with this product I decided I should. I paid $37 and change and fully expected to get my money's worth (and that's not that much money if you know what I mean) but I needed a toy organizer and the colors were right. Anyways, this organizer included 12 bins which are very sturdy, not thin plastic and a very nice quality. You get four large and they are plenty big and nine med/small which hold enough... All together it is amazing how much you really can get stored with all 12. The stand had to be put together but it took me about fifteen minutes and is pretty self explanatory but it did come with included picture instructions. Once it was all put together I was happy to see it is only 15 inches deep so it hardly takes up any room in a small bedroom (much less room than toys all over the floor! The height of the organizer is perfect for my three year old to see what's in each bin and playing and returning the toys to thier new home is almost a much fun as just playing now. I purchased the multi color and it came with a nice pastel shade of green,pink, yellow and blue bins.The colors are quite nice and don't look cheap. I highly recommend this bin organizer and I feel like the price I just got it at was a steal for the quality.

reviews.reviewText: We needed some more organization for our toddlers things in the play area and found these to help teach him organization and cleaning up after yourself.The rack assembled really quickly (just use a drill and zip zip) plenty of storage and allows you to break the toys up to how you would want them to be organized on the shelf and the best part is that it is toddler sized so they can pick up their own toys.This worked out great.

reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Good size and a lot of buckets
reviews.reviewText: The colors are cute pastels. The buckets are deep but due to the slant you can’t fill them to the top (which my kids love to do) or the toys spill out. And it’s a bit wobbly. We try to tighten it but to no avail. Still using it a year later though so definitely worth the price!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 16, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Clutter-Free Playtime Bliss with Humble Crew Toy Organizer!
reviews.reviewText: The Humble Crew Grey/White Kids Toy Organizer has transformed our play area into a haven of organization and convenience! As a parent, keeping toys tidy and easily accessible is a constant challenge, but this organizer has proven to be an absolute game-changer.The sleek grey and white design seamlessly blends into any room decor, adding a touch of modernity to the play space. The organizer comes with 12 spacious bins in various sizes, providing ample storage for a variety of toys – from building blocks to stuffed animals. The versatility of the bins allows for easy categorization, making cleanup a breeze.Assembly is a stress-free experience, and the sturdy construction ensures the durability of the organizer. The bins are made from high-quality materials that can withstand the energetic play of toddlers. The compact size is ideal for smaller spaces, and the low height allows even the littlest ones to access their toys independently.What sets this toy organizer apart is its practicality. The bins are easily removable, allowing kids to take out and put away toys with ease. The clear plastic material of the bins makes it simple to identify the contents at a glance, promoting a sense of order and making it easier for kids to find what they're looking for.The Humble Crew Kids Toy Organizer has brought a sense of order and calm to our play area. It's not just a storage solution; it's a tool that encourages responsibility and independence in kids. If you're a parent in need of a stylish, functional, and kid-friendly toy organizer, look no further – this is the one that checks all the boxes!
